en_883794_0	Colombo (News1st): 2891 Police Officers have been given promotions.
en_883794_1	Police Media Spokesperson SP Ruwan Gunasekera said the promotions were given following interviews carried out over the recent weeks.
en_883794_2	1783 Police Constables have been promoted to the rank of Police Sergeant while 334 Female Constables have been promoted to the rank of Sergeant.
en_883794_3	553 Police Sergeants have been promoted to the rank of Sub Inspector of Police, this also included 76 female sergeants.
en_883794_4	124 Officers have been promoted from Police Constable Driver to Police Sergeant Driver.
